            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM1_CONTENT_VIEWING_PROPERTY3: 'S3.Other websites where users or website operators are permitted to embed the Video Player; and',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM1_CONTENT_VIEWING_PROPERTY4: 'S4.YipTV authorized applications, features or devices.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM1_DESCRIPTION1: 'SUse of the YipTV Services (including access to the Content) on the Properties is subject to compliance with these Terms of Use ("Terms of Use" or "Terms") and any end user license agreement that might accompany a YipTV application, feature or device.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM1_DESCRIPTION2: 'SCertain YipTV Services are provided to you free-of-charge. There are some other YipTV Services that, if you are interested in accessing, will require payment by you. The YipTV Services that may be accessed after payment are referred to currently as "YipTV." You can learn more about YipTV by visiting YipTV.com/plus. There is certain information in these Terms that relate only to YipTV and those specific provisions are set forth in Section 4 below. Accordingly, if you choose to subscribe to YipTV, then please familiarize yourself with Section 4, in addition to all of the other provisions in these Terms (please note that references to "YipTV Services" throughout this Terms of Use are intended to include YipTV). If you are not a subscriber of YipTV, then Section 4 does not apply to you.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM1_DESCRIPTION3: 'SIt is our pleasure to provide the YipTV Services for your personal enjoyment and entertainment in accordance with these Terms of Use. To access and enjoy the YipTV Services, you must agree to, and follow, the terms and conditions set forth in these Terms of Use. By visiting the YipTV Site or using any of the YipTV Services (including accessing any Content) you are agreeing to these Terms. Please take a moment to carefully read through these Terms. It is our goal to provide you with a first class user experience, so if you have any questions or comments about these Terms, please contact us at: legal@yiptv.com',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM2_TITLE: 'S2. CHANGES TO THE TERMS OF USE BY YIPTV',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM2_DESCRIPTION:'SYipTV may amend these Terms of Use at any time by posting the amended Terms of Use on the YipTV Site at yiptv.com/terms. If we make a material amendment to these Terms of Use, we will notify you by posting notice of the amendment on the YipTV Site. Any material amendment to these Terms of Use shall be effective automatically 30 days after it is initially posted or, for users who register or otherwise provide opt-in consent during this 30 day period, at the time of registration or consent, as applicable.',
